{
  "stem": "26983.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was my former head of our school, Mr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Robin. ?] I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I remember-- shortly before, I visited the headmistress of our school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was Mrs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Sifer. ?] She was a very old-- in my eyes at that time-- an old lady.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was living in a-- at that time, before the deportation from Mahrisch Ostrau-- in an old parents' home or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And was so shocked for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's a symbol of the best is suddenly in an old parents' home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And later on, I saw her in Theresienstadt, which was even a terrible shock for me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Just before the deportation, when once they took 10,000 of elderly people and sent them away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she was sitting alone, with her number, and waiting to be taken to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was unforgettable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- at that time, we knew only to the east.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were deported to the east.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I will try to tell you about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just before Theresienstadt, I told you they took all kinds of things from us-- the jewelry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to help the German soldiers-- Winterhilfswerk-- WHW-- to give all warm clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even the walking sticks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, every family at the time had walking sticks and we had it from the mountains with all these kinds of signs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to give it away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this walking stick-- somehow, I had very many memory, because I met them again in many other places.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Auschwitz and even in the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But now we gave everything away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the transport came, and we came to this place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to give away our personal identification card or whatever we had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was stamped, liquidiert, liquidated.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
